{"tid":1430335,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香城online新職業 — 聯絡兵","createTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-08T02:18:27.000Z","uid":263452,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6210f4dc91cb2346c346908d16b03cdd7f572995","tid":1430335,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:19.000Z","msg":"原來舊po開錯係時事台<br />\n唔怪得無人推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實個職一D都唔新<br />\n不過<span style=\"color: red;\">好重要</span>同<span style=\"color: red;\">好缺人</span><br />\n舊post有略略介紹過<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1373707/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1373707/page/1</a><br />\n<br />\n近日個OL玩家唔興打BOSS轉型快閃<br />\n聯絡兵需求同重要性同時大左好多<br />\n8月3號到8月5號都不斷轉場<br />\n浮現左一個大問題<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔知轉場轉去邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bang.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n有D發夢人士可能依家就明我想講咩<br />\n大概解釋下就係:<br />\n當叫轉場時<br />\n所有人同時向同一方向走係會塞死<br />\n所以好多時會分左唔同方向唔到時間走<br />\n散開成幾十批人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">而每批人同其他人都係無聯絡</span><br />\n就算有都係只有其中一兩批<br />\n咁當本身轉場去支援個場D人都轉場<br />\n結果就有一隊隊人企係原地瘋狂望公海/聯絡其他朋友<br />\n再重新FC討論決定<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">無FD子散開/有消息FC唔到/無消息就直接off左一班人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n我地想做既野係<br />\n幫手<span style=\"color: red;\">connect</span>起唔到組既人<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">真正做到「一方有難，八方支援」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n職位都有分 冷氣軍師 同 現場通訊<br />\n好多手足<span style=\"color: red;\">有心想幫手但只能睇live</span><br />\n都可以做<span style=\"color: red;\">真點冷氣軍師</span>幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n首先講返我哋每個職業嘅定位 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1.現場哨兵</span><br />\n要做既野:<br />\n行路時:其實無咩<br />\n起防線及守城時:幫手將冷氣軍師整合好既資訊發放比前排玩家(主要係前排)<br />\n當前排玩家有決定時將決定PM比另一條防線既好友 <br />\n再轉達比其他防線 <br />\n令佢地有足夠資訊去做好決定<br />\n轉副本時:離開本身個副本時玩家會四散 而我地就要散係唔同位connect返佢地 比佢地可以隔空討論 再有轉場共識<br />\np.s.可以自己簡前定後 dress code跟返大隊/有自己做法都可<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">2.冷氣軍師</span><br />\n整合 <br />\n有陣時前線睇唔切手機或者現場哨兵睇唔切手機 <br />\n整合嗰邊可以整合一啲有用嘅訊息例如逃生路線等等<br />\n適量簡化整合每一條小組既決定+live資料<br />\n直接畀現場隊員<br />\n<br />\nplanning <br />\n呢個係要事前規劃定有幾多個plan <br />\n當遇上某種情況就plan a另一種情況plan B <br />\n再由現場人士將個plan建議比前線<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">勿做大台!!!</span></span><br />\n<br />\n地圖  <br />\n呢個首選熟悉野外定向人士<br />\n去幫手留意住現場可以走到嘅路線同埋狗隻推進ge路線 <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">放風公海</span><br />\n歡迎入黎比意見討論下<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/IPz9axOq2Y53BvtAFkTxOg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FIPz9axOq2Y53BvtAFkTxOg&d=zO4uXE7qxnklPfV4Vu9eJeDrFCZ%2FFQqiuLijmhCLlc8%3D&h=cbbaf98c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/IPz9axOq2Y53BvtAFkTxOg</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">我就唔信我地connect曬仲會輸比班黑社會popo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n同堆唔該幫手推po"},{"pid":"dc3af68a1ef0afd2654c408b7486b9fa642d1e92","tid":1430335,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:35.000Z","msg":"1/10"},{"pid":"87ead5778d85456488203d7bb1ed11a101442c8a","tid":1430335,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:46.000Z","msg":"2/10"},{"pid":"d00f9cba0cd7bc0071edecacdae3a82eea187a92","tid":1430335,"uid":263452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-07T17:09:56.000Z","msg":"3/10"},{"pid":"45cd33a7095a0cbc3fd2d6ecadfd2cabf6f25b11","tid":1430335,"uid":199739,"like":0,"d